1. Upon successful authorization, the catalog opens.
2. If the data is entered incorrectly, an error appears
3. If you click on the add item to cart button, the item should fit in the cart.
4. The shopping cart must contain a description of the product (price, information about the product)
5. When you click on the basket, the basket should open
6. It should be possible to remove an item from the cart and from the catalog
7. When making a purchase, you must fill in all the fields, in case of incorrectly entered data, a corresponding message should be displayed